snippet.title: Ynxa Prologue Atari Lynx gameplay
snippet.description:
Ynxa is a new game coming to Atari Lynx

Here is small footage of gameplay : helping Leaf to unlock Air Powers during the Prologue.

Play as Leaf, unlock the powers of Air, Fire and Water, prove your bravery through the 8 paths of Perseverance, then explore the Pyramid and the underworld to find the 5 ceremonial objects.

https://yastuna-games.com/en/2-home?q=Categories-Ynxa
